  "prompt": "How do I delete snapchat conversation without using clear conversations?",
  "response": "To delete a Snapchat conversation without using the \"Clear Conversations\" feature, you can follow these steps:\n\n1. **Open the Snapchat app** on your device.\n2. **Swipe right** to access the Chat screen.\n3. **Locate the conversation** you want to delete.\n4. **Press and hold** on the conversation, which will bring up a menu.\n5. Select **\"More\"** from the menu options.\n6. Tap on **\"Delete Chats...\"**.\n7. You will be given options to \"Delete\" or \"Cancel\". Choose **\"Delete\"**.\n\nPlease note that this will delete the conversation from your chat list, but it won't delete it from the other person's chat list. Additionally, if there are saved messages in the conversation, those will not be deleted unless both parties unsave them.",
